title: Area Codes in Ohio
name: Area Codes in Ohio
description:
Telephone area code boundaries of Ohio

Created by dissolving telephone exchange boundaries which had been digitized  from 24,000 scale USGS topographic maps.  The ArcGIS Dissolve command was used to eliminate boundaries between exchanges with the same area code.  The data incorporates several changes which have been made to the area code definitions since the data was originally created.
